    <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dromara/fast-request/master/screenshot/searchEveryWhere.png" /><br/>
    <h2>API manager</h2>
    <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dromara/fast-request/master/screenshot/apis.png" /><br/>
